Bottle is a fast, simple and lightweight WSGI micro web-framework
for Python. It is distributed as a single file module and has no
dependencies other than the Python Standard Library. Features:

  * Routing: Requests to function-call mapping with support for
    clean and dynamic URLs.

  * Templates: Fast and pythonic built-in template engine and support
    for mako, jinja2 and cheetah templates.

  * Utilities: Convenient access to form data, file uploads, cookies,
    headers and other HTTP-related metadata.

  * Server: Built-in HTTP development server and support for paste,
    fapws3, bjoern, Google App Engine, cherrypy or any other WSGI
    capable HTTP server.
